        <mxCell id="flegend" value="Notes:&#xa;• cron at /api/bot/followups, every 15 minutes&#xa;• cadence = elapsed since last_follow_up_at exceeds stage threshold (1h / 2h / daily)&#xa;• counter resets on customer inbound (handled in /api/bridge/webhook, not here)&#xa;• stop-word in inbound text → escalate + pause immediately (webhook side)&#xa;• WAITING_FACTORY is Eli-only: customer is left in silence, Eli gets daily reminder to chase factory&#xa;• templates live in lib/messaging/templates.ts (deterministic strings; LLM polish later)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
